{{ProductPage|https://www.iogear.com/product/GWU637/}} While the FCC photos are not sufficient, this device appears to be RTL8198 based. This would suggest that the ethernet port is actually 10/100/1000 despite IOGear's claim of 10/100 speeds in the listed specs.
